      "patchset_number": 4,
      "line": 88,
      "message": "Let's do this in single map call. It will look a little bit uglier, but we have to remember about thread safety. `Reader` is \"very stateful\" (tm) ;-) so we probably should avoid passing it in the reactive stream.\n\n\"very stateful\" - not only we can change it put almost any method call may result in a race condition",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 2683,
        "name": "Piotr Jaszczyk",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "piotr.jaszczyk@nokia.com",
        "username": "jaszczur"
